The paper discusses a decentralized access control mechanism using blockchain technology for space situation awareness. This involves authentication and access control for devices, services, and information in a decentralized and heterogeneous system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
